{"tid":1840423,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"中產同草根家庭子女逗既利是","createTime":"2020-01-24T21:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T01:00:07.000Z","uid":99883,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"09abb51ff9da0e07434cdb26fde9290d9ec29c2f","tid":1840423,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:46:54.000Z","msg":"中產家庭子女：20年前屋企人利是每封$500，20年後每封$1000，甚至結埋婚做派利是果個。親戚部分係高學歷，就算係低學歷，都有自己既生意，有頭腦，有返d投資營商心得。過完年拆利是總數至少都接近$5000。<br />\n<br />\n草根家庭子女：20年前屋企人利是$100，20年後都係$100 (其實係畀多左家用屋企人封利是，轉手畀返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。婚就唔敢結，甚至有冇女都成問題，學生時期，哪有錢冧女吃喝玩樂？親戚個個唔係廢佬就係廢婆，低學歷，周身病痛，無業，退休，要依賴仔女養。過完年拆利是封封都係$20，總數$1000都冇，拆都廢撚事。"},{"pid":"20327bab6f55aa16f8927e158fd9eba4e68524f2","tid":1840423,"uid":336046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:50:49.000Z","msg":"相信有最好嘅父母都會俾你<br />\n但如果自己冇能力帶俾小朋友好日子嘅 咁又何苦要生"},{"pid":"59692da7c3bb7b0806c5e1cca7b142403c63369e","tid":1840423,"uid":28068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T21:58:28.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前每年有800-1000<br />\n近兩三年得500-600<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c448bdcf1e09df1199e837cba8ebd470eb56cf6","tid":1840423,"uid":94502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:02:41.000Z","msg":"中產都得幾百點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc181be06b1e9d891d4ce8f35ff88d096737b6fb","tid":1840423,"uid":138981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:14:54.000Z","msg":"想當年某個親戚得嗰十歲嗰時佢收咗一封廿萬利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52033371092e1548291dd89e2e6d9a8526d2c139","tid":1840423,"uid":232731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T22:17:33.000Z","msg":"我年年都係一樣，親戚每個至少派1千，老母老豆各1皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /